image_analysis.description: A photograph of a small kitchen or kitchenette area. It features white upper and lower cabinetry, a stainless steel sink set into a white countertop, and a black and white checkered tile floor. A stainless steel range hood is mounted on the wall to the left of the upper cabinets. A roll of paper towels is mounted under the upper cabinets. A flexible hose or pipe is visible on the right side of the counter, extending towards the floor. The walls are painted a light cream or yellow color.
image_analysis.layout: The image is a vertical shot of a kitchen corner, showing the floor, lower cabinets, countertop, upper cabinets, and a range hood.
